1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Your 3 PM crash
is not about food.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
You ate a normal lunch. You slept okay.
So why are you dead by 3?

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Your biological alertness dips 7-9 hours after waking.
It's a circadian signal, not a fuel problem.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:25,000
10 minutes of bright light around noon. Walk
outside. Look up. It resets the dip.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Link in bio — free
energy profile in 30 seconds.

